    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Continuous roof covering of laminations or piles of saturated or coated felt, alternated with layers of bitumen and surfaced with mineral aggregate or asphaltic material.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
